    "        | Layer | Component |\n",
    "        |-------|-----------|\n",
    "        | 1. ILS Engine | Felder-Silverman 4-dimension learning style model |\n",
    "        | 2. Dataset | ILS-personalized JSONL, 80/10/10 split, diversity metrics |\n",
